{"tid":140178,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"扮牧師稱遺失銀包呃好心人 75歲積犯判囚4周","createTime":"2017-03-02T04:09:41.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-02T08:44:15.000Z","uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"da28e98bf24dd393832ea92019a1775eb9379fe4","tid":140178,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T04:09:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/02/120858_53f19e52b6a6360f12dff763de949409.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F02%2F120858_53f19e52b6a6360f12dff763de949409.jpg&h=b1530db6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n被告林韜10年前曾以同樣手法犯案(資料圖片)<br />\n過往有26次涉及不誠實案底紀錄的老翁，去年11月1日中午，於半山羅便臣道向女途人自稱元朗一所中學的牧師，正帶一班學生到中區遊覽，但卻意外遺失銀包，向女途人借款500元。女途人不虞有詐向他借錢，但未幾已覺可疑，於是致電學校查詢，發現被騙後即報警。<br />\n<br />\n老翁林韜（75歲）當日在案發現場附近被拘捕，今在裁判法院承認以欺騙手段取得財物罪。控方指被告過往有30次案底紀錄，其中26次涉及不誠實，最後一次犯案是10年前。<br />\n<br />\n裁判官指雖然被告認罪、事主沒有損失，但以案件性質理應判囚，終判被告入獄4周。<br />\n<br />\n被告律師求情指，被告在案發後10分鐘已打算將錢歸還事主，但未及還錢已被捕，而事主最終沒有損失，而且金額不大，希望判緩刑。<br />\n<br />\n被告10年前曾在中環向途人冒認醫生，稱要帶一班學生到長洲考急救試，但意外遺失銀包，而向途人襄借4,200元，被告及後認罪被判入獄8個月。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56374290&amp;category_guid=6996647&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170302\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56374290%26category_guid%3D6996647%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170302&d=DXsCe6mrroMB06wP0eqGVYsQCuff2cTRbXvS6e969MQ%3D&h=470a7e9d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56374290%26category_guid%3D6996647%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170302&h=6a28c675\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56374290&amp;category_guid=6996647&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170302</a>"},{"pid":"ccd8cc78b1c2f262ca8a563cd804645e487b9636","tid":140178,"uid":30487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T04:14:36.000Z","msg":"呃鳩啲左膠錢就啱啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21b52bf5111c4157824184c17c2421d43ba48e61","tid":140178,"uid":36142,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T08:39:01.000Z","msg":"30次案底<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"295eb8f1bdfbfb170b52f003aef6eedd02409c77","tid":140178,"uid":49853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T08:44:15.000Z","msg":"咁多次案底都係判四週<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我覺得多過三次案底應該要double刑期"}]}